race.comment: WEST ON RICKY (1) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (23.11) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can make amends this time. CLEARY MAGIC (6) failed to threaten in two average runs to date. Bold showing expected. SMELL LIKE ROSE (2) is a newcomer from the Enzo Crudeli kennel. Drawn well and should get her chance. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance. Something for the Multiples: DODGY SHADOW (5)
